---
---

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-image-wrap" data-animate="left">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503387762-592deb58ef4e?w=800&q=80"
        alt="KN Architects team reviewing architectural plans"
        loading="lazy"
        width="600"
        height="700"
      />
      <div class="about-accent-border"></div>
      <div class="about-badge">
        <strong>10+</strong>
        <span>Years of Excellence</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content" data-animate="right">
      <span class="section-label">About Us</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Building Dreams<br />Since 2014</h2>
      <p class="about-body">
        Founded in the heart of Chennai, KN Architects & Builders was born from a singular passion: to create spaces that endure. For over a decade, we have been transforming visions into living reality — from intimate family homes in Tambaram to landmark commercial developments across Tamil Nadu.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        Our philosophy is rooted in the belief that great architecture is not merely about aesthetics, but about how a space makes you feel — every morning, every evening, for decades to come. We blend modern design sensibilities with structural integrity, delivering projects on time and on budget without compromise.
      </p>
      <p class="about-body">
        From blueprints to brickwork, from structural engineering to the finest interior finishes, we manage every dimension of your project with the precision it deserves.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="about-link">
        Begin Your Project
        <svg width="20" height="8" viewBox="0 0 20 8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M0 4h18M14 1l4 3-4 3"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: var(--section-pad) 5vw;
  }
  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Image side */
  .about-image-wrap {
    position: relative;
  }
  .about-image-wrap img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 580px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-accent-border {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -18px; right: -18px;
    width: 140px; height: 140px;
    border: 2px solid var(--red);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 36px; left: -28px;
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(196,30,30,0.4);
  }
  .about-badge strong {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .about-badge span {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Content side */
  .about-content { color: var(--charcoal); }
  .about-content .section-heading {
    color: var(--black-deep);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  .about-body {
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: #3a3a3a;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
  }
  .about-link:hover { gap: 1.2rem; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .about-image-wrap img { height: 420px; }
    .about-badge { left: 0; }
  }
</style>
